{"article_id":"sewdu6dfM2xUALOc","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The Justice Department ' s inspector general has submitted a criminal referral for former FBI Deputy Director Andrew McCabe ,","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"according to CNN ' s Pamela Brown .","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"Inspector General Michael Horowitz ,","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"who submitted a harsh report","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"asserting","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"that McCabe misled Justice Department investigators last week ,","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"has referred the matter to the US attorney ' s office in Washington , DC , for potential prosecution .","depth":3},{"id":7,"text":"Yet","depth":4},{"id":8,"text":"though McCabe has been harshly criticized by President Donald Trump and his allies for months for supposed anti-Trump bias ,","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"he ' s been investigated for and may be charged about a different topic entirely -","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"that is , his purported attempts to mislead about his role in a leak at Hillary Clinton ' s expense .","depth":5},{"id":11,"text":"The gist is that McCabe orchestrated a leak to a Wall Street Journal reporter shortly before the 2016 election ,","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"describing private deliberations","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"he ' d had","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"with Obama Justice Department officials about an investigation of the Clinton Foundation .","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"McCabe leaked","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"that he had tried to keep this investigation moving forward , over an unnamed Justice Department official ' s resistance .","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"His motivation","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"for leaking about this pending investigation ,","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"it appeared ,","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"was to rebut an earlier Journal article","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"raising questions about his impartiality in the Clinton email probe , and a planned follow-up piece along similar lines .","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"However ,","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"once the FBI began looking into how the Clinton Foundation leak happened ,","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"Horowitz claims","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"that McCabe repeatedly misled officials about his involvement .","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"The IG report says","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"McCabe displayed a \" lack of candor \" on the topic on at least four separate occasions","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"- falsely claiming several times","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"that he didn ' t know","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"where the leak had come from ,","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"when in fact he had authorized it .","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"The Justice Department says","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"it was these findings","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"- not Trump ' s fury at and angry tweets about McCabe -","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"that spurred Attorney General Jeff Sessions ' s controversial firing of McCabe","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"one day","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"before he was set to retire .","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"And it ' s these findings","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"that would likely form the basis of any charges against McCabe ,","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"should the US attorney for the District of Columbia choose to pursue them .","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"McCabe has been trying to portray himself as corruptly and wrongly persecuted by President Trump for political and self-interested reasons ,","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"suggesting","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"Trump hopes to discredit potential testimony from him in special counsel Robert Mueller ' s probe of obstruction of justice .","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"Indeed , the president has aimed a truly astonishing level of vitriol at McCabe ,","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"and the news comes in the context","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"of Trump allies in Congress","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"calling for the prosecution of not just McCabe but multiple Justice Department officials as well as Clinton herself .","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"Still , the allegations against McCabe in the IG report are quite serious ,","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"inspectors general traditionally operate with independence from their department leaders ,","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"and Horowitz was appointed under President Obama .","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"So it ' s too simple to say that McCabe is just being railroaded here .","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"If he did indeed lie to investigators ,","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"that ' s criminal conduct .","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"To understand the full scope of what ' s going on here ,","depth":6},{"id":55,"text":"it ' s useful to separate out President Trump ' s gripes with Andrew McCabe from the inspector general ' s critique of Andrew McCabe","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"- because they ' re quite different .","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"Trump ' s distrust for McCabe personally seems to date back to the revelation","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"that","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"when McCabe ' s wife ran for Virginia state Senate in 2015 ,","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"the state ' s Democratic governor , longtime Clinton ally Terry McAuliffe , raised money for her campaign .","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"After the election","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"( she lost ) ,","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"McCabe was involved in overseeing the Clinton email investigation ,","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"and conservatives questioned","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"whether this was a conflict .","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"Trump would later cite this information repeatedly , both in public and in private ,","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"as showing McCabe ' s supposed corruption .","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"( McCabe actually voted in the Republican primary in his state , Virginia , in 2016 . )","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"More broadly , though , Trump has been at war with his own FBI and Justice Department","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"since he fired James Comey .","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"He has repeatedly urged the department to charge his political and bureaucratic opponents with crimes .","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"McCabe , as a Comey ally and career staffer , was a natural obstacle .","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"There ' s also been speculation","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"that Trump hopes to discredit McCabe as a potential witness to obstruction of justice in the Mueller probe .","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"So Trump openly campaigned for McCabe ' s firing for months ,","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"and exulted","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"when it finally happened .","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"Andrew McCabe FIRED , a great day for the hard working men and women of the FBI","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"-","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"A great day for Democracy .","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"Sanctimonious James Comey was his boss","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"and made McCabe look like a choirboy .","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"He knew all about the lies and corruption","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"going on at the highest levels of the FBI !","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":7},{"id":86,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":7},{"id":87,"text":"March 17 , 2018","depth":6},{"id":88,"text":"Yet you could follow everything","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"Trump has said about McCabe for months","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"and have no real understanding","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"that he was fired","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"for allegedly lying about his leaks about an investigation into Hillary Clinton .","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"The IG says","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"McCabe misled investigators about a pre-election leak about Clinton","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"On October 24 , 2016 , the Wall Street Journal ' s Devlin Barrett published that story about McCabe ' s wife getting campaign contributions from McAuliffe ,","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"pointing out","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"that McCabe had a role","depth":12},{"id":98,"text":"overseeing the Clinton email investigation .","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"Then on October 30 , Barrett published another story .","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"His sources describe , in some detail , interactions","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"McCabe was said to have had with Obama Justice Department officials about an investigation of the Clinton Foundation .","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"It portrays McCabe as heroically trying to keep this investigation moving forward , over an unnamed Justice Department official ' s resistance .","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"McCabe has now admitted to authorizing these leaks .","depth":8},{"id":104,"text":"And they were serious ones :","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"They described internal deliberations about an ongoing investigation","depth":11},{"id":106,"text":"tied to a major-party presidential nominee","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"and were let out just before a presidential election .","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"The motivation now seems obvious :","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"They were designed","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"to prevent damage to McCabe and the FBI ' s reputation from Barrett ' s earlier article","depth":12},{"id":111,"text":"( and a follow-up piece","depth":13},{"id":112,"text":"he was working on )","depth":13},{"id":113,"text":"by portraying McCabe as tough on Clinton ,","depth":12},{"id":114,"text":"and offering a juicy anecdote","depth":13},{"id":115,"text":"to prove it .","depth":13},{"id":116,"text":"But the inspector general report claims","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"that McCabe later displayed \" lack of candor \" to FBI and Justice Department officials about his role in these leaks , in at least four instances .","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"To Comey on October 31 , 2016 :","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"The day after the latter Journal article published ,","depth":12},{"id":120,"text":"Comey and McCabe privately discussed it and the leaks behind it .","depth":12},{"id":121,"text":"Comey later told the inspector general","depth":12},{"id":122,"text":"that McCabe left the impression","depth":13},{"id":123,"text":"that he wasn ' t involved in the leak","depth":14},{"id":124,"text":"and he didn ' t know","depth":15},{"id":125,"text":"who was .","depth":15},{"id":126,"text":"McCabe disputes this ,","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"claiming","depth":11},{"id":128,"text":"he fessed up to Comey ,","depth":12},{"id":129,"text":"and that Comey agreed","depth":13},{"id":130,"text":"the leak was a \" good \" idea .","depth":13},{"id":131,"text":"The IG writes","depth":9},{"id":132,"text":"that the \" overwhelming weight \" of circumstantial evidence backs up Comey ' s account , not McCabe ' s .","depth":9},{"id":133,"text":"To the FBI ' s Inspection Division investigators on May 9 , 2017 :","depth":10},{"id":134,"text":"A few months later , two FBI investigators questioned McCabe about the article ,","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"and asked about the leaks .","depth":12},{"id":136,"text":"The agents claim","depth":12},{"id":137,"text":"McCabe told them","depth":13},{"id":138,"text":"he had \" no idea \"","depth":15},{"id":139,"text":"where the story came from or who the source was","depth":15},{"id":140,"text":"- which , of course , would be a lie .","depth":14},{"id":141,"text":"McCabe disputes","depth":11},{"id":142,"text":"that this happened ,","depth":12},{"id":143,"text":"and the interview wasn ' t recorded .","depth":12},{"id":144,"text":"But both agents say","depth":11},{"id":145,"text":"this happened ,","depth":12},{"id":146,"text":"one of them took notes ,","depth":13},{"id":147,"text":"and they got McCabe to sign his initials on the Journal article ,","depth":14},{"id":148,"text":"indicating","depth":15},{"id":149,"text":"that the topic was discussed .","depth":15},{"id":150,"text":"To the IG investigators on July 28 , 2017 :","depth":11},{"id":151,"text":"Later , investigators from the inspector general ' s office questioned McCabe in a recorded interview ,","depth":13},{"id":152,"text":"and presented him with texts from his subordinate Lisa Page","depth":13},{"id":153,"text":"indicating","depth":13},{"id":154,"text":"that she was involved in the leak .","depth":13},{"id":155,"text":"McCabe said","depth":11},{"id":156,"text":"he didn ' t know","depth":13},{"id":157,"text":"who gave the information to the Wall Street Journal","depth":13},{"id":158,"text":"and that he wasn ' t aware of her being authorized to do it .","depth":12},{"id":159,"text":"However , a few days after saying this ,","depth":12},{"id":160,"text":"McCabe contacted investigators","depth":12},{"id":161,"text":"and said","depth":12},{"id":162,"text":"that","depth":13},{"id":163,"text":"after thinking about it more ,","depth":14},{"id":164,"text":"he may have authorized the leak after all .","depth":14},{"id":165,"text":"( Marcy Wheeler suggests","depth":11},{"id":166,"text":"that McCabe ' s change of heart came","depth":12},{"id":167,"text":"because he realized","depth":13},{"id":168,"text":"those texts from Page made his previous , false story","depth":15},{"id":169,"text":"disclaiming knowledge of the leak","depth":15},{"id":170,"text":"untenable . )","depth":14},{"id":171,"text":"To the IG investigators again on November 29 , 2017 :","depth":11},{"id":172,"text":"McCabe returned for another recorded interview with IG investigators ,","depth":12},{"id":173,"text":"this time admitting his role in the leak .","depth":12},{"id":174,"text":"Yet Horowitz says","depth":11},{"id":175,"text":"he misled them about other matters .","depth":11},{"id":176,"text":"McCabe said in this interview","depth":12},{"id":177,"text":"that he ' d told Comey about the leak","depth":13},{"id":178,"text":"and that Comey was okay with it on October 31 , 2016 ,","depth":13},{"id":179,"text":"and claimed","depth":12},{"id":180,"text":"he never denied knowledge of the leaks to FBI investigators on May 9 , 2017 .","depth":12},{"id":181,"text":"Yet Horowitz doesn ' t find either claim to be credible .","depth":10},{"id":182,"text":"From the report , Horowitz clearly believes","depth":10},{"id":183,"text":"that McCabe tried to avoid being fingered for the leak","depth":11},{"id":184,"text":"by repeatedly misleading investigators and even Comey , his boss , about it .","depth":11},{"id":185,"text":"It is this report","depth":12},{"id":186,"text":"that Horowitz submitted to the FBI","depth":12},{"id":187,"text":"and that the Justice Department cited","depth":12},{"id":188,"text":"in firing McCabe in March ,","depth":12},{"id":189,"text":"and that is reportedly the basis for the criminal referral .","depth":10},{"id":190,"text":"President Trump ' s opinions about McCabe are obviously widely known .","depth":8},{"id":191,"text":"Yet there is no indication","depth":9},{"id":192,"text":"that Horowitz ,","depth":12},{"id":193,"text":"whose role is as an internal watchdog","depth":13},{"id":194,"text":"and who ' s been in the job since 2012 ,","depth":13},{"id":195,"text":"distorted his investigation","depth":11},{"id":196,"text":"to try to please the president .","depth":10},{"id":197,"text":"If McCabe truly did","depth":9},{"id":198,"text":"what Horowitz asserts ,","depth":9},{"id":199,"text":"it would certainly be a firing offense","depth":9},{"id":200,"text":"and may well be criminal too .","depth":9},{"id":201,"text":"McCabe has denied wrongdoing .","depth":6},{"id":202,"text":"His lawyer , Michael Bromwich , released a statement","depth":7},{"id":203,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":204,"text":"he is \" confident","depth":9},{"id":205,"text":"that ,","depth":10},{"id":206,"text":"unless there is inappropriate pressure from high levels of the Administration ,","depth":11},{"id":207,"text":"the US Attorney ' s Office will conclude","depth":12},{"id":208,"text":"that it should decline to prosecute. \"","depth":12},{"id":209,"text":"A GoFundMe page for McCabe ' s legal defense raised $ 567,996 last month .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":419,"left":216,"right":418,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":216,"left":211,"right":215,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":211,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":215,"left":214,"right":6,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":214,"left":2,"right":213,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":213,"left":3,"right":212,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":212,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":418,"left":249,"right":417,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":249,"left":219,"right":248,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":219,"left":7,"right":218,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":218,"left":217,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":217,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":248,"left":239,"right":247,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":239,"left":229,"right":238,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":229,"left":224,"right":228,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":224,"left":222,"right":223,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":222,"left":11,"right":221,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":221,"left":220,"right":14,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":220,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":223,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":228,"left":226,"right":227,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":226,"left":17,"right":225,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":225,"left":18,"right":19,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":227,"left":20,"right":21,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":238,"left":232,"right":237,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":232,"left":22,"right":231,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":231,"left":23,"right":230,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":230,"left":24,"right":25,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":237,"left":26,"right":236,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":236,"left":27,"right":235,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":235,"left":234,"right":31,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":234,"left":28,"right":233,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":233,"left":29,"right":30,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":247,"left":244,"right":246,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":244,"left":32,"right":243,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":243,"left":240,"right":242,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":240,"left":33,"right":34,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":242,"left":35,"right":241,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":241,"left":36,"right":37,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":246,"left":38,"right":245,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":245,"left":39,"right":40,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":417,"left":295,"right":416,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":295,"left":264,"right":294,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":264,"left":261,"right":263,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":261,"left":251,"right":260,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":251,"left":41,"right":250,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":250,"left":42,"right":43,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":260,"left":254,"right":259,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":254,"left":44,"right":253,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"